    <item>
      <title>How I Built a Secure To-Do App with XSS Protection</title>
      <link>https://mrdruv.github.io/Blog-XSS_Todo/blog/my-first-post/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 May 2025 12:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://mrdruv.github.io/Blog-XSS_Todo/blog/my-first-post/</guid>
      <description>
        
        
        &lt;p&gt;Hey folks! üëã &lt;br&gt;
In this post, I‚Äôll walk you through how I built a simple to-do list app using just plain JavaScript ‚Äî no frameworks, no dependencies, just vanilla JS. I‚Äôll also touch on how I made it safe from common security threats like XSS (Cross-Site Scripting).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Let‚Äôs dive in!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;üéØThe Goal&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;the-goal&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#the-goal&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;I wanted to create a To-do list where:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Users can enter the tasks and click enter to add it.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Clicking on tasks reveals extra options like setting due dates and adding notes .&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Users can even delete the tasks.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;üß†Key Concepts&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;key-concepts&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#key-concepts&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;The app covers:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;DOM manipulation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Event handling&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Dynamic rendering&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Input validation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;XSS protection via HTML escaping&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Let give quick intro on this concepts.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1.DOM manipulation:&lt;/strong&gt;
DOM(Document Object Model) Manipulation refers to changing HTML or content of web page using Javascript.You can add,remove or modify elements dynamically after page loaded.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2. Event handling:&lt;/strong&gt;
Event handling means listening for actions like clicks,typing and form submissions, and then responding to them with code.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;3. Dynamic rendering:&lt;/strong&gt;
Dynamic rendering means updating parts of the web page automatically as the user interacts, without reloading the page.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;4. Input validation:&lt;/strong&gt;
Input validation checks if user input is correct before processing it ‚Äî like making sure a name field isn&amp;rsquo;t empty or an email is formatted properly.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;5. XSS Protection via HTML escaping:&lt;/strong&gt;
Cross-Site Scripting (XSS) is when attackers inject malicious JavaScript into your site. To prevent this, you escape special characters in user input before adding it to the DOM.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;üß© The HTML Structure&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;-the-html-structure&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#-the-html-structure&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;I use two main elements in DOM:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-block hx-relative hx-mt-6 first:hx-mt-0 hx-group/code&#34;&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-javascript&#34; data-lang=&#34;javascript&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nx&#34;&gt;input&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;nx&#34;&gt;id&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s2&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;taskInput&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;nx&#34;&gt;type&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s2&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;text&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;nx&#34;&gt;placeholder&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s2&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;Add a task...&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;/&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nx&#34;&gt;ul&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;nx&#34;&gt;id&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s2&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;taskList&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;/ul&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn-container hx-opacity-0 hx-transition group-hover/code:hx-opacity-100 hx-flex hx-gap-1 hx-absolute hx-m-[11px] hx-right-0 hx-top-0&#34;&gt;
  &lt;button
